title: Yegor Kryshtafovich
text:
Yegor Nikolayevich Kryshtafovich (; born 17 October 1980) is a Russian former professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a>er.
Club career.
He played 7 seasons in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Baltika%20Kaliningrad">FC Baltika Kaliningrad</a>.
